00:42:35,083 --> 00:42:36,292
The last of them

551
00:42:36,958 --> 00:42:38,708
was Cardinal Spada.

552
00:42:40,333 --> 00:42:45,083
At the end of his life,
sheltered on the island of Monte-Cristo,

553
00:42:46,500 --> 00:42:49,542
