to train one last knight.

554
00:42:51,375 --> 00:42:53,292
This young man was called...

555
00:42:53,917 --> 00:42:55,583
Giuseppe Faria.

556
00:42:59,542 --> 00:43:02,500
I am the last survivor, Edmond.

557
00:43:03,458 --> 00:43:05,208
And I know

