600
00:46:10,375 --> 00:46:12,167
-The treasure exists.

601
00:46:13,792 --> 00:46:15,375
You know where to find it.

602
00:46:16,333 --> 00:46:18,667
-We will go look for it together!

603
00:46:18,833 --> 00:46:20,083
-Don't forget.

